description.narrative: This activity (HABS Project Support Staff) is a component of Helmand Area Based Stabilisation reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £696,455. This component benefits Afghanistan, and works in the following sector(s): Civilian peace-building, conflict prevention and resolution. The start date is 01-05-2008 and the end date is 31-03-2012.
